Display.SelectFromListDialog.SelectItemsFromList Title: $'''Search queries''' Message: $'''What searches do you want to perform?''' List: SearchQueries IsTopMost: False AllowEmpty: False PreSelectItemsWithPlus: False SelectedItems=> SelectedSearchQueries
LOOP FOREACH EntireSearchValue IN SelectedSearchQueries
    WebAutomation.LaunchChrome.LaunchChrome Url: $'''https://www.bing.com/search?q=%EntireSearchValue%''' WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Maximized ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> Browser
    WebAutomation.ExtractData.ExtractList BrowserInstance: Browser Control: $'''html > body > div:eq(1) > main > ol > li''' ExtractionParameters: {[$'''div:eq(0) > h2 > a''', $'''Href''', $'''%''%'''] } PostProcessData: False TimeoutInSeconds: 60 ExtractedData=> SiteLinks
    WebAutomation.CloseWebBrowser BrowserInstance: Browser
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation TextToWrite: $'''%EntireSearchValue% site links:''' AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation TextToWrite: SiteLinks AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
    # Start of autogenerated actions using the recorder
    WebAutomation.LaunchChrome.LaunchChrome Url: $'''https://duckduckgo.com/?q=%EntireSearchValue% site:youtube.com&t=h_&iax=videos&ia=videos''' WindowState: WebAutomation.BrowserWindowState.Normal ClearCache: False ClearCookies: False WaitForPageToLoadTimeout: 60 Timeout: 60 BrowserInstance=> Browser
    WebAutomation.GetDetailsOfElement BrowserInstance: Browser Control: appmask['Recording']['Anchor'] AttributeName: $'''href''' AttributeValue=> YoutubeSiteLink
    # End of autogenerated actions using the recorder
    WebAutomation.CloseWebBrowser BrowserInstance: Browser
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation TextToWrite: $'''%EntireSearchValue% Youtube site link:''' AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation TextToWrite: YoutubeSiteLink AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
    File.WriteText File: FileSaveLocation AppendNewLine: True IfFileExists: File.IfFileExists.Append Encoding: File.FileEncoding.Unicode
END
